603
01:12:54,375 --> 01:12:59,369
l don't get it. Miklós is always
giving me shit,

604
01:12:59,495 --> 01:13:05,730
in the band he plays all instruments,

605
01:13:05,975 --> 01:13:08,011
he is driving me crazy.

606
01:13:09,775 --> 01:13:11,174
l'm scared.

607
01:13:11,415 --> 01:13:12,814
l'd like to screw someone.

608
01:13:16,975 --> 01:13:18,408
l wanted to breed dogs...

609
01:13:18,495 --> 01:13:20,611
l was admitted finally...

610
01:13:43,695 --> 01:13:47,927
Excuse me...
Doc... hey, wait...

611
01:13:49,295 --> 01:13:52,492
How much?
l'll buy it, okay?

612
