Okay, okay, okay, okay...

613
01:14:11,295 --> 01:14:13,684
Relax!

614
01:14:18,775 --> 01:14:20,891
- What happened?
- Self defense.

615
01:14:22,135 --> 01:14:24,569
- We don't beat up passengers.
- She kicked me in the nuts.

616
01:14:24,655 --> 01:14:28,443
- Only after you grabbed me.
- You're a psycho bitch.

617
01:14:29,015 --> 01:14:31,575
l'll take care of this...

618
