l'm reporting this, Bulcsú.

619
01:14:34,535 --> 01:14:38,084
What are you going to report?
That a teddy bear attacked you?

620
01:14:38,175 --> 01:14:40,814
Teddy bear?
She is an aggressive animal.

621
01:14:40,895 --> 01:14:42,613
Behind me.

622
01:14:42,775 --> 01:14:44,174
Come!

623
01:14:45,695 --> 01:14:47,413
Margit!

624
01:14:48,615 --> 01:14:50,651
Where were you?

625
01:15:09,895 --> 01:15:13,649
You! You want to go up
and get a coffee?

626
01:15:23,015 --> 01:15:25,404
You're working. l understand.

627
01:15:29,335 --> 01:15:32,930
- l know a nice place close by.
- What?

628
01:15:33,175 --> 01:15:37,612
- A nice place down here.
- Now l can hear you.

629
01:15:43,775 --> 01:15:46,243
l'll buy you coffee.

630
01:15:47,055 --> 01:15:48,852
Okay.

631
01:16:10,455 --> 01:16:12,252
Sugar?

632
01:16:14,815 --> 01:16:18,410
Nice place.
Come here often?

633
01:16:19,335 --> 01:16:22,691
Only when l really want
to impress a girl.

634
01:16:28,455 --> 01:16:30,411
Thanks.

635
01:16:36,455 --> 01:16:39,288
You like working down here?

636
01:16:41,175 --> 01:16:43,769
You kind of get used to it.

637
01:16:48,535 --> 01:16:51,493
l never thought about it.

638
01:16:52,255 --> 01:16:54,325
What?

639
01:16:55,575 --> 01:16:59,090
lt must be tough for you guys.

640
01:17:01,255 --> 01:17:04,088
