have come looking for you.

671
01:24:39,015 --> 01:24:41,085
Sit down.

672
01:24:41,175 --> 01:24:44,485
Do you have any requests
before we start?

673
01:24:46,375 --> 01:24:49,014
May l have a glass of water?

674
01:24:54,775 --> 01:24:58,051
What happened this afternoon?

675
01:24:59,895 --> 01:25:02,887
Look at the tapes.

676
01:25:03,535 --> 01:25:05,844
